  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Gill's Exposition of the Entire Bible",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "For the hurt of the daughter of my people am I hurt,.... These are the words, not of God, as Jerom; nor of Jerusalem, as the Targum; but of the prophet, as Kimchi observes, expressing his sympathy with the people in their affliction: and they may be rendered, \"for the breach of the daughter of my people\" (o), which was made when the city was broken up and destroyed, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Jeremiah 52:7",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "I am broken; in heart and spirit: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "I am black; with grief and sorrow. The Targum is, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "\"my face is covered with blackness, black as a pot.'' ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Astonishment hath taken hold on me; at the miseries that were come upon his people; and there was no remedy for them, which occasion the following words. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "(o)  \"super contritione\", V. L. Pagninus, Montanus; \"super confractione\", Schmidt; \"ob fractionem\", Cocceius. ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "(o)  \"super contritione\", V. L. Pagninus, Montanus; \"super confractione\", Schmidt; \"ob fractionem\", Cocceius. ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
